---

---

<section
  id="nan-madol"
  class="reveal flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[560px] bg-sand-bright"
>
  <a id="history" class="sr-only">History anchor</a>
  <div class="md:w-1/2 relative overflow-hidden bg-basalt">
    <img
      class="w-full h-full object-cover min-h-[360px]"
      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doruy2kdr/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_1400,h_900/feature-nan-madol-step-into.jpg"
      alt="Nan Madol — ancient basalt walls"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
  <div
    class="md:w-1/2 p-10 md:p-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-start tapa-pattern border-l border-basalt/5 relative"
  >
    <span
      class="font-label text-ochre tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[11px] font-semibold mb-5"
    >
      Nan Madol · A UNESCO World Heritage Site
    </span>
    <h2
      class="font-headline text-basalt text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.03] mb-7 tracking-tight max-w-xl"
    >
      A lost city <em class="italic text-ochre">in the sea</em>.
    </h2>
    <p
      class="font-body text-basalt/75 mb-9 leading-relaxed max-w-md text-[15px]"
    >
      You get there by boat. The channel narrows, the mangroves close in, and
      then the walls appear — massive basalt columns stacked six centuries ago
      on artificial islands in the middle of a lagoon.
    </p>
    <p
      class="font-body text-basalt/75 mb-9 leading-relaxed max-w-md text-[15px]"
    >
      Nan Madol was the seat of the Saudeleur Dynasty, a political and
      ceremonial complex built across 92 islets connected by tidal canals.
      It's now a UNESCO World Heritage Site — and still one of the most
      difficult-to-reach major archaeological sites on Earth.
    </p>
    <p
      class="font-body text-basalt/60 italic mb-9 leading-relaxed max-w-md text-[15px]"
    >
      That's part of what makes it worth it.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/plan-your-trip"
      class="group flex items-center gap-4 text-ochre font-headline text-lg hover:text-ochre-deep transition-colors"
    >
      Plan a Visit to Nan Madol
      <span
        class="w-12 h-px bg-ochre transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-20"
      ></span>
      <span class="font-body text-xl">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
